Package org.apache.sis.storage.earthobservation

@Deprecated package org.apache.sis.storage.earthobservation
Deprecated.
Moved to org.apache.sis.storage.landsat.
Metadata readers for some format used in Earth observation (Landsat, MODIS). This package includes mapping from the following formats to ISO 19115 metadata:
Earth observation formats
Format Provider Apache SIS notes
Landsat 8 level 1 U.S. Geological Survey (USGS) Mapping from/to ISO 19115

1.1
